Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.61,0:01:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{破られた退部届}Episode 009\NTorn resignation letters
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.03,0:01:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{みどりさん。}Midori-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.84,0:01:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{いよいよあたしたちの出番が来たようね。}At last it's time for our turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.93,0:01:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{え。}Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.56,0:01:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{出番？}Your turn?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.19,0:01:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{どう言う意味？}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.63,0:02:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{それはこの前のを返しをさせてもらうことよ。}We want to repay you for the last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.52,0:02:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{何ですって？}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.54,0:02:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{強がりを止しなさいよ。}Drop the act.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.03,0:02:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{いくらやっても、同じこと。}The results won't change.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.06,0:02:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{二人共さ、休みの間にあたしたちXXなったって言うの？え？}Or maybe you've spent your spring break on some special training?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.92,0:02:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{まさか。ヘヘヘ。}As if, hahaha.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.68,0:02:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{その通りよ。}That's exactly right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.82,0:02:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{ね、エープリルフールは過ぎたのよ。}Hey, April Fools is long over.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.32,0:02:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{言っとくけどさ、この前実力で勝ったんですからね。}Just to make it clear: we've already proved our skill before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.51,0:02:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{お分かり？}Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.16,0:02:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{だから実力XXX返しようと言うの。}That's why we want to repay you with skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.29,0:02:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{分かる？}Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.16,0:02:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{あなたたちにね…何時までも大きな顔させないてこと。分かる？}We won't let you keep that boastful attitude forever. Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.68,0:02:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{よく分かったわ。}We get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.14,0:02:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{どうやら、もう一度可愛がるほか成せそうだわね。}Looks like the last time wasn't enough for you after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.55,0:02:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{フン。}Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.90,0:02:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{馬鹿馬鹿しいじゃん。四天王XXXこんな(XXX・練習試合)にするなんて。}That's ridiculous. Our Big Four is too good to accept such a request.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.33,0:02:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{だからさ。ぐうの音もでないようにしてやるんだ。}No trash talk. We'll play with them all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.44,0:02:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{へ？}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.36,0:02:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{ファイト同じメンバーでいいのね。}We'll play with the same people.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.99,0:02:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{さ、いらっしゃい。}You've got your game.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.00,0:02:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{良いわね。}Happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.02,0:02:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{ーやろう。\Nーなによ。}- Let's do this.\N- What's with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.33,0:02:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{畜生。}Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.97,0:02:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{やるの？}Are we really doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.26,0:02:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ。本郷先生だわ。}Ah, it's professor Hongou.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.62,0:03:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{先生！}Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.61,0:03:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{ー先生！\Nー先生！}- Professor!\N- Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.01,0:03:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{先生、富士見の生徒XXXために来たんですか？}Professor, did you come to be Fujimi students' good charm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.88,0:03:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{何？}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.59,0:03:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしたちの梶岡先生下ろして、コーチに売り込んだ。そういうつもりなんでしょうね。}You've taken place of our professor Kajioka as the new coach to promote yourself, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.05,0:03:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{ま。}Whoa…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.02,0:03:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{なに言ってるの。}What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.22,0:03:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{そんな本郷先生じゃないのよ。}Professor Hongou is not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.96,0:03:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{じゃ、なぜ無理にコーチに成ろうとしたのよ。}Then why did he push to become our coach?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.66,0:03:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{泉さん…}Izumi-san…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.37,0:03:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{フン！黙って！}Hmph. Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.67,0:03:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{泉さん、どうしたんだろう。}I wonder what's with Izumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.36,0:03:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{何かが変よ。}She's acting strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.21,0:03:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{許せないわ。}I won't forgive it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.32,0:03:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{バレー部員としてあたしたちを除け者にしようなんて…}As the club members, for you to cast us out…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.84,0:03:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{どう言うことなのよ？}What do you intend to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.34,0:03:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{先生。}Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.16,0:03:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{何とか言ったらどうなんです？}How about you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.18,0:03:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうよ。本郷先生。}That's right. Professor Hongou.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.87,0:03:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{こんな人怒鳴りつけて…}She's yelling so much…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.21,0:03:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{XXX・思い出したと驚かないわよ。}You two stay out of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.30,0:03:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{ちょっと、先生！}What it'll be, professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.72,0:03:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{何だ、その言い方は。}What's with your way of talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.24,0:03:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{生徒は先生に大して聞く口じゃないな。}Students these days have no respect at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.81,0:03:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{だが、ま良い。}Never mind that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.88,0:03:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{こんなことと言っても、君達は勝手に今日XXだろう。}Even if you say this, you come here as you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.69,0:04:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{俺に言えるはただ一つ。}I will say just this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.12,0:04:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{バレー部はバレーの実力は第一だ。}In the volleyball, the skill is the most important.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.89,0:04:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{所で、その実力でお返しすると言っただようだが？}By the way, I believe you said you want a grudge match.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.63,0:04:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}That's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.38,0:04:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{言いました。}We did.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.11,0:04:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{ー親分…\Nーだって、あたしじゃん…}- Chief…\N- We're no good…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.53,0:04:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{面白いわ。}Interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.63,0:04:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{それじゃ、あんたたち…}Well then, you girls…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.88,0:04:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{本郷先生の前でゆっくりとその実力を見せてもらいましょうね。}…let's see your skills before your beloved professor Hongou.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.84,0:04:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{どうする？}What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.62,0:04:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{まあまあことないよ。}It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.74,0:04:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{先生が言ったんだもん。勝ってんかってにやっつけちゃうよ。}The teacher nailed it. We'll just kick their butts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.65,0:04:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{早く。}Hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.09,0:04:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{ま。やろうやろう。}Let's do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.83,0:04:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{実力でお返しすると言った、君達の言葉を信じよう。}"Repay with skill." I'll believe those words.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.36,0:04:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{頼むぞ、鮎原。}I'm counting on you, Ayuhara.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.70,0:04:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{鮎原さん、一歩一歩一本。}Ayuhara-san, take your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.06,0:04:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{ー頑張ってね！\Nーキャプテン。}- Do your best!\N- Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.38,0:04:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{えい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.30,0:04:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{XXX}I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.87,0:04:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{ーあ！\Nーお！}- Ah!\N- Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.71,0:04:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{変化球。}The curve ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.60,0:04:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{「木の葉落とし」。}"Leaf Fall".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.72,0:04:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{フフン。}Hehe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.44,0:04:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{へへへ。}Fufufu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.28,0:05:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{何よぼやぼやしてるの？}Why are you spacing out?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.46,0:05:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{ポイントよ、得点。}It's a point for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.60,0:05:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{得点をXXX。}We scored one point.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.74,0:05:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{はーはい、ただいま。}Y-yes ma'am! Right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.36,0:05:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{泉組・鮎原組}《Izumi group: 0》\N《Ayuhara group: 0》
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.24,0:05:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{泉組・鮎原組}《Izumi group: 0》\N《Ayuhara group: 1》
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.52,0:05:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{行くわよ。}Here I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.95,0:05:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{それ！}Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.83,0:05:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{だ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.82,0:05:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ…}Ah…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.60,0:05:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{アン。}Ahh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.22,0:05:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{あぁ…}Ahh…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.83,0:05:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{痛い。}It hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.85,0:05:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{痛い…}It hurts!…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.78,0:05:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{又手が痺れた…}My hand got numb again…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.24,0:05:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{どうしよう？}What to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.78,0:05:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.30,0:05:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ、泉さん！}Ah, Izumi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.63,0:05:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ…}Ah…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.98,0:05:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{わい、キャプテン！いいぞ、いいぞ！}Waii, captain! Nice, nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.67,0:05:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{鮎原さん、すこしXXXやったら？}Ayuhara-san, maybe we should go easy on them?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.50,0:05:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{わい、(XXX・いいね、ふたり、いいね)。}Waii, good going, good going!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.10,0:05:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{わあい！}Waai!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.34,0:05:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{行くわよ。}Here I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.65,0:05:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{えい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.46,0:05:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.33,0:05:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{XXX}Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.41,0:05:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ！}Ah!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.31,0:05:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{ほ？}Ho?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.97,0:05:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{鮎原所か、早川であの変化球サーブを…}Besides Ayuhara, Hayakawa can serve that curve ball too…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.10,0:05:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{鮎原さんだけの変化球と思った、間違いよ。}If you thought I'd lose to Ayuhara-san, big mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.64,0:05:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{いかが？}How do you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.71,0:05:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{早川さん、すごい！}Hayakawa-san, awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.41,0:05:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{信じられないわ。}I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.88,0:05:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{こんなに調子良く決まるなんて不思議なくらいだわ。}It feels so strange when we're leading this easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.11,0:06:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{合宿XXこんなに覿面だなんて…}I didn't think the camp would be this effective.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.83,0:06:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{でも、あたしたち以上面食らってるのはあそこにいるわ。}But looks like our surprise can't compare with theirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.01,0:06:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{んん。}Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.44,0:06:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{鮎原さん。}Ayuhara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.47,0:06:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{負けたくない。}I don't want to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.02,0:06:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{負けられないわ。}I can't lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.27,0:06:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{絶対に。}Never.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.36,0:06:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.23,0:06:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{負けるもんか！}No way we'll lose!…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.75,0:06:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.27,0:06:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{負けるもんか！}No way we'll lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.07,0:06:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{負けるもんか！}No way we'll lose!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.39,0:06:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{泉は無理になって、調子を崩している。}Izumi became unreasonable and lost her rhythm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.32,0:06:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.08,0:06:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.20,0:06:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{ーはい。\Nーそれ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.47,0:06:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ！}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.60,0:06:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{あぁぁ！}Aaa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.18,0:06:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい、セットいただきよ！}All right! We won this set!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.94,0:06:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{わい、YYY皆YYY！}Waai, you did well!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.83,0:06:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ、痛い。}Ah, it hurts…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.50,0:06:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{親分、すごい。}Chief, that was terrific.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.59,0:06:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{左手あんなに打てるなんてさ！}The way you served with your left hand…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.49,0:06:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{それも強烈！コートは(XXX・凹みそうな)スパイクね。}And that strength. That spike could dent the court.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.58,0:06:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{どう？今の鮎原さんの実力よ？}How did you like current Ayuhara-san's skills?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.92,0:06:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{フン。}Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.20,0:06:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{ん…}Uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.77,0:06:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{ん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.51,0:06:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{負けたわ。}We lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.51,0:07:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{どうーどうして？未だ勝負がこれからよ。}Wh- what are you saying? The match starts now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.39,0:07:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{ワンセット終わったばかりじゃない…}It's ridiculous to decide it with a single set…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.37,0:07:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{弱き出さないで、泉さん。}Stay strong, Izumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.08,0:07:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{ーあ、泉さん…\Nー泉さん。}- Ah, Izumi-san.\N- Izumi-san…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.43,0:07:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{泉くん！}Izumi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.20,0:07:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{どうしたんだ、泉？}What's wrong, Izumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.79,0:07:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{もう駄目よ。}It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.18,0:07:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{この手が言うこと聞かないわ。}This hand just won't react.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.69,0:07:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{ー泉さん！\Nー泉さん！}- Izumi-san!\N- Izumi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.21,0:07:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{ー泉さん。\Nー泉さんたら…}- Izumi-san.\N- Izumi-san, hey…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.20,0:07:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{泉さん。}Izumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.84,0:07:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{なぜ途中でXXX？泉さんらしくないわね。}Why did we give up midway? That's not like you, Izumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.46,0:07:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{何セットやっても、同じことよ。}Any more sets wouldn't change the outcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.74,0:07:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{ーえ？\Nーえ？}- Eh?\N- Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.68,0:07:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{そんな…}But why…?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.10,0:07:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{そんなバカな…}That's ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.70,0:08:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしには分かってるんだ。}Don't argue with me. I know what I'm talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.28,0:08:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{悔しいけど、先に帰るわ。}It's regrettable. I'll be going home first.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.25,0:08:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{ん…}Hm…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.60,0:08:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{どうかしてるんじゃない？}That was crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.88,0:08:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ、泉さんらしくないわ。}Ah, it's so unlike Izumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.84,0:08:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{なるほど。}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.91,0:08:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{大学の合宿に参加したのか。}So it was university training camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.68,0:08:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{道理で。}That explains it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.02,0:08:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{しかし、辛かったろう。}But it must've been tough, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.01,0:08:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.54,0:08:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{でも、四天王に勝ったですもの。}But we won with the Big Four.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.56,0:08:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{すかっとしました。}I feel refreshed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.91,0:08:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{親分てんでススーパーマンだったわよ。}Chief, you were like Superman.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.94,0:08:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{早川さんだって、あんな変化球出すなんて…}Hayakawa-san's curve ball was awesome, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.53,0:08:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{本当、格好良かったわ。}Yeah. It was super cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.87,0:08:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{これでやっとあたしたちのバレー部らしく成った}It finally feels like volleyball club again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.96,0:08:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうよ。二度とあんなやつに口じゃさせないわ。}Yeah. I don't want to hear their boasting ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.26,0:08:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{天狗の鼻を折られて、ぺっちゃんこ。}They couldn't see past the end of their noses.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.15,0:08:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{ざまあご覧、遊ばせって。}In the end they had to bump into a wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.02,0:08:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{ハハハハ。}Hahahaha.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.34,0:08:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{ヘヘヘ。}Heheheh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.54,0:08:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{ああ…}Aah…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.74,0:08:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{お終いだわ、四天王もう。}The Big Four is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.01,0:08:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{だが、鮎原。}However, Ayuhara…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.07,0:09:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{これから一体どうするつもりだ？}…what do you want to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.12,0:09:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{え？}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.76,0:09:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{四天王…このまま仲間外れにしておくのうかない？}Don't you want to fix your relationship with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.27,0:09:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{鮎原達ともかく、他のメンバーと比べたら彼女達の方がはるかに実力は上だ。}With the exception of Ayuhara's group, when compared to other members, they are stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.80,0:09:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{それは君達を認めるな。}I'm sure you understand that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.47,0:09:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{だって、先生。}But professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.65,0:09:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{あんな非協力的な人たちとチーム組むなんてあたしたちはできないわ。}It's futile for us to try joining forces with such uncooperative people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.59,0:09:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{ヘヘヘ。}Hehehe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.69,0:09:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{できるかできんかは、それはま、君達に任せよう。}Futile or not, I'm entrusting it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.42,0:09:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{良いな？鮎原。早川。}God it? Ayuhara. Hayakawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.37,0:09:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{ね？香取さん、どうするのよ。}Katori-san, what will it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.24,0:09:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{んん。}Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.22,0:09:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{あなたたちがその気なら、しょうがないな。}If you feel this way, it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.79,0:09:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{じゃ、決まった。}It's decided then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.83,0:09:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{泉さんに話して、明日は四人一緒に退部届けよう。}After telling Izumi-san, let's put our resignation together tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.21,0:09:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{了解。}Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.21,0:09:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{誰があんなバレー部いてやるもんですか。}Who'd want to be in that club anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.46,0:09:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{(XXX・黄線)だ!}Keep it straight!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.78,0:10:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{ファイト、ファイト！}Fight, fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.54,0:10:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{ぼやぼやするな！}Don't space out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.54,0:10:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{良く玉を見ろ！}Watch the ball closely!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.05,0:10:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{先生あんなこと言うけど、}No matter what professor said…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.61,0:10:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{無理よね。}…it's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.76,0:10:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{無理って？}What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.13,0:10:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{四天王きっと止めちゃうわ、バレー部を。}The Big Four are sure to quit the club now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.51,0:10:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{やめさせるわけにはいかないわ。}We can't let them do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.74,0:10:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしたち先じゃ大変な戦力低下よ。}Our power will fall considerably.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.18,0:10:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{弱気な、鮎原さん。}That's weak, Ayuhara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.60,0:10:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{四天王なんかいなくだって、あたしたちって十分やっていけるわ。}Even without the Big Four we're plenty capable on our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.47,0:10:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ、それはどうかしら。}Ah, I wonder about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.74,0:10:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{今の泉さん何とか変だもの。}Izumi-san acted strange today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.27,0:10:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{あれは実力と思えないわ。}I can't believe she gave it all she had.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.40,0:10:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{とにかく、明日もう一度話してみるわ。}At any rate, I'll try talking to them tomorrow again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.28,0:10:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{無駄よ、無駄。}It's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.35,0:10:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{退部直ぐに決まってます。}I'm positive they'll drop out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.10,0:10:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{んん。絶対に退部させないわ。}I absolutely won't let them do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.50,0:10:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{ー強情ね。\Nーあなたこそ。}- You're so stubborn.\N- Same goes to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.42,0:10:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{へへ。}Hehe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.20,0:10:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{いいや、XXX。}I'm trying to be a realist.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.52,0:10:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{キャプテンにお任せするわ。}I'll leave it to you, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.32,0:10:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{やってみる。}I'll take my chances.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.63,0:11:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしの力で四天王を説得してみせる。}I'll show you that I can persuade the Big Four.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.06,0:11:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{ああ。}Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.34,0:11:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{さ、それで三人の退部届は揃ったわけない。}Well then, now that we have our letters ready…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.05,0:11:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{ね、泉さんは？}Where's Izumi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.98,0:11:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{それはさ、お休みらしいの。}Seems like she's absent today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.75,0:11:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{どうせ、退部届らすなら四人に一緒にと思ったのに。}I thought we'd deliver the letters with all four of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.16,0:11:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{一体どうしたかしら、泉さん。}I wonder what happened to Izumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.17,0:11:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{昨日のショックは大きいなのね。}Yesterdays game must've gotten to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.07,0:11:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{きっと。}Surely.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.74,0:11:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{《泉》}《Izumi family》
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.12,0:11:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{いや。}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.68,0:11:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{ゆり。}Yuri…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.50,0:11:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{いやったら、いや。}By "no" I mean "no".
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.47,0:11:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{大の病院なんかいつもんですか、絶対いや。}I don't want to go to the hospital again.{ZZZ}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.33,0:11:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{だって、とても痛そうじゃないの。}But it looks very painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.49,0:11:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{その腕で試合をするなんて無茶ですよ。}Playing more with that arm is reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.71,0:11:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{ね。}Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.52,0:11:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{さ、早く。}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.69,0:11:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{お母さんも一緒に来ますから。ね？}I'll go with you, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.09,0:11:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{そんなに行きたきゃ、お母さん一人で行けば良いじゃない。}If you want to go that much, then go without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.42,0:11:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしはいやよ。}I'm not going there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.82,0:11:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{ゆり！}Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.05,0:11:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{お待ちに…！}Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.29,0:11:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{ゆり！}Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.16,0:12:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{で、君には説得する自身があるのか？}So, do you think you'll be able to persuade them?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.41,0:12:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{んん。それで実は困ってるの。}Hm. To be honest, I'm not really sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.65,0:12:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{ね、何か良い考えないかしら。}Hey, maybe you can think of something?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.83,0:12:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{昨日は弾みであんなこと言っちゃったけど、正直などこはあの人達と仲良くする何てできそうにないんもね。}I said that in the heat of the moment yesterday, but I honestly don't think I can make friends with these girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.47,0:12:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{だけど、君達だって、四天王だって…バレーを愛することに軽いはないんだろ。}But both you and the Big Four share the love for the volleyball, don't you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.35,0:12:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{それはもちろんよ。}Of course we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.01,0:12:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{それだったらさ…なぜチームが組めれないんだよ。}Why can't you join forces then?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.85,0:12:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{君達のどっかに誤解なるとしか考えられないね。}I can't help but think you've misunderstood each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.97,0:12:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{世の中には虫が付かないってこともあるわ。}In this world there are things that even bugs won't touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.62,0:12:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{へへ。}Hehe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.55,0:12:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{大体、君は頭にXXXだからな。}You can be harsh at times, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.17,0:12:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{ん。}Hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.79,0:12:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{それに、早川くんの時だって、殴り合い寸前に成ったそうじゃないか。}I just remembered how you almost got in a fight with Hayakawa-san in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.97,0:12:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ、いやだ、知ってたの？}Ah, you knew it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.50,0:12:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{さすが新聞部は早耳ね。}That's a newspaper club member for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.22,0:12:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ。}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.99,0:12:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ、あなたたち…}Ah… you girls…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.80,0:12:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{は。}Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.67,0:13:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{鮎原さん。}Ayuhara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.56,0:13:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{ー色々お世話になりました。\Nーへ？}- Sorry for all the trouble.\N- Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.98,0:13:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{ーあたしたちはバレー部を辞めるの。\Nーま。}- We're quitting the volleyball club.\N- Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.83,0:13:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{ほら、この通り見てよ。}See for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.84,0:13:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{退部届よ。今本郷先生に持ってく途中。}It's a resignation letter. We're on the way to professor Hongou.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.66,0:13:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{そんな…}That's too bad…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.91,0:13:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{あなたたち、バレーに命をかけていたじゃないの。それなのに…}You girls, haven't you staked everything on the volleyball so far? If that's the case…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.37,0:13:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{命をかけた？ご冗談でしょう。}"Staked everything"? Don't be absurd.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.69,0:13:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{あんなボール遊び何か…}For such a stupid ball game…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.07,0:13:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{嘘！}You're not serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.19,0:13:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしには分かるわ。}I understand it more than you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.85,0:13:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{あなた方は嘘を付いてるの。}There's no way you're thinking that seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.52,0:13:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{バレーバカに成ったあたしだから分かるわ。}I'm a fool for volleyball too, so I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.53,0:13:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{遊び半分の練習で、あなたたちほどの実力は付く分けないわ。}Training half for fun, unlike you, I can't get better.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.19,0:13:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうでしょう？}Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.44,0:13:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{フフフ。その実力者を破ったXXXは、天才だとでも言いたいの。}Fufufu. In other words, you're telling us we're geniuses?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.90,0:13:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{何ですって？}What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.03,0:13:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{さ、行きましょうよ。}All right, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.86,0:13:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{待って！}Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.21,0:13:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{意地を張るのは止して。ね？}Don't be stubborn… please?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.09,0:13:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{ーよく考えて…\NーXXXたくさんよ。}- Please think it ove-\N- We've had enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.95,0:13:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{ー行こう、行こう。\Nー行こう。}Let's go, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.56,0:13:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{このままでしておいて良いのか？}Is it okay to let them go like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.44,0:14:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{待って！待って！}Wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.63,0:14:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{な、何よ。}What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.73,0:14:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{な…！}Wh-!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.45,0:14:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{何するのよ！}What are you doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.36,0:14:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{ーちょっと返してよ！\Nー返してよ！待ちな！}Hey, give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.73,0:14:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{返してよ！}Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.97,0:14:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{早く返してよ！}Get over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.47,0:14:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{へ。鮎原くんは掻っ払いXXXしらなかったな。}Oh, I didn't know Ayuhara-san can handle paperwork well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.71,0:14:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{《３年c組》}《Class 3C》
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.57,0:14:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{まったく人をバカにしてやりかたね。}What a way to make a person look like a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.54,0:14:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{このまま放っとくてはないわ。}We can't let her off the hook like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.67,0:14:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{あんたたちやらなきゃ、あたしだけでもやる。}If you don't do something, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.65,0:14:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうよ。黙ってられもんですか。}Yeah. I won't be staying silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.64,0:14:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{香取さん。あんたは？}Katori-san. What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.06,0:14:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{そ…それは、あたしだって。}We- well, same goes for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.11,0:14:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{よし。}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.83,0:14:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{どっか呼び出そう。}Let's notify someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.00,0:14:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{富士見のXXからなんかどう？}How about the principal?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.25,0:14:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{良いわ。}Sounds good. {あたしはそう行ってくる。}I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.73,0:14:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ。}Ah, it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.58,0:14:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{ちょうどよかったわ。}Good timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.88,0:14:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{工藤さん。あなたたちにちょっと話があるんだけど。}Kudou-san. I want to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.02,0:14:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{ー話？\Nーえ。}- Talk…?\N- Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.27,0:14:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{授業が終わったら、富士見川のXXX来て。}Come to see me by the riverbank after classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.75,0:14:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{待ってるわ。きっとよ。}I'll be waiting. It's a promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.17,0:14:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{鮎原さん！}Ayuhara-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.93,0:15:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{臭う、XXX。}Damn it, she left me no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.07,0:15:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{XXX}We're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.04,0:15:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{どこにだれが隠れてるか知りやしないわ。}Be prepared for a company.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.00,0:15:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{XXX静かね。}It's awfully quiet…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.71,0:15:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{相手は何人来てるよ？}How many people will be there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.43,0:15:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{そんなこと分かる分けないでしょう。}There's no way we can know it…!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.49,0:15:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{他の人は良いから、鮎原だけをマークして。}Never mind the others and focus on Ayuhara.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.71,0:15:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{良いわね。}Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.54,0:15:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{いらっしゃい。}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.38,0:16:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ。}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.39,0:16:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{遅かったわね。}You're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.76,0:16:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{あんた、一人？}Are you alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.78,0:16:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうよ。なぜ？}Yes. Why are you asking?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.66,0:16:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{じゃ、どうしたあたしたちを呼び出したのよ。}Then why have you called us here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.31,0:16:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{聞きたいことがあっただから。}There's something I wanted to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.36,0:16:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{これよ。}It's about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.46,0:16:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{な、何よ！}Wh- what is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.41,0:16:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{言ってごらんなさいよ。}Let's hear whatever it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.56,0:16:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{あなたたちは本当にバレー部を辞めるつもり？}Do you really want to quit the volleyball club?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.12,0:16:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{ん。もちろんよ。当たり前じゃないの？}Of course we do. Isn't that obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.33,0:16:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしはあなたたちと争ってだけど…}I may have fought with you until now…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.62,0:16:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{でもあなたたちの力を尊敬していたわ。}…but I have always respected your talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.10,0:16:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{フン。}Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.39,0:16:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{フン。}Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.13,0:16:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたくしだも鮎原さんのサーブとスパイクを尊敬しておりますのよ。}I respect your serve and spike too, Ayuhara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.74,0:16:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{でしょう？}Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.58,0:16:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{そのあたしとあなたたちは力を合わせたら、すごいチームに成ると思うけどな。}If me and you join our forces, we might make an excellent team together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.27,0:16:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{へ？}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.62,0:16:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{本気でそう思ってるの？}Are you serious about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.32,0:16:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{もちろん。}Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.42,0:16:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{だって、同じバレーをやりからには、試合に勝ちたいわ。}We're in the same club and I want to win matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.10,0:16:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{少しでも…少しでも強いチームを作りたいでしょう?}Don't you want to make a strong team even a little bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.33,0:16:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{同じバレーをやるからには？}We're in the same club?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.42,0:16:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{フン。}Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.09,0:16:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{お生憎様。}Too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.33,0:17:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしたち…二度とバレーボールを見るXXいやよ。}We don't want to see a volleyball ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.97,0:17:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{じゃ、どうしても退部届よ？}So you're dropping out no matter what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.07,0:17:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{え。}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.03,0:17:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{返してよ、退部届。}Hand over the letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.56,0:17:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{あんたはいくらじゃましたって、あたしたちは辞めるわ。}No matter how much you disturb us, I'm quitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.12,0:17:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{バレーボールなんか糞XXXだわ。}To hell with volleyball.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.10,0:17:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{返してよ。}Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.65,0:17:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{ー返して。\Nー返して。\Nー返して。}Give it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.00,0:17:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{ー返すのよ。\Nー返すのよ。\Nー返すのよ。}Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.75,0:17:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ…}Ah…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.13,0:17:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{な、何すんのよ。}Wha- what are you doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.28,0:17:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ…}Ah…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.95,0:17:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{そんなにバレーが憎いなら、こうしてボールを裂いてごらんなさい。}If you hate volleyball that much, let's see you cut up that ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.78,0:17:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{見にのもういやなボールならずだずだにしてごらんなさいよ。}Let's see you tear that ball you don't want to see ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.86,0:17:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{それができたら、あたしは諦めて退部届きを返しするわ。}If you can do it, I'll give it up and give you the letters back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.37,0:17:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{フン。}Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.65,0:17:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{バレーが何よ…}Who needs volleyball.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.35,0:17:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{バレーが何よ！}Who needs volleyball!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.66,0:18:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{こんなもの…}Such a thing…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.00,0:18:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{何よ…こんなもの…}Who needs that thing…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.08,0:18:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{バレーが何よ！}Who needs it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.49,0:18:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{ボールが何よ！}Who needs this ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.63,0:18:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{ボールが泣くわ。}The ball is crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.35,0:18:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{泣いてるわ。}It's crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.13,0:18:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{ボールは昨日まであなたの親友だったのね。}Until yesterday, that ball was your true friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.51,0:18:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{あなたはその親友をXXXとしている。}Now you're trying to cut that friend to pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.18,0:18:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{煩い！}Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.53,0:18:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{辞めて！}Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.66,0:18:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{危ない！}Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.48,0:18:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{フン…}Uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.89,0:19:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしには…}I…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.50,0:19:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしにはできないわ。}I couldn't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.46,0:19:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{浜紀中学に入る時に誓ったじゃないの？}Didn't we promise after entering Hamaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.06,0:19:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{小沢さんも…小沢さんも。大学へ進んでまで必ずバレーボールを続けるって…}Kudou-san… Ozawa-san… we promised we'll continue with volleyball till high school…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.92,0:19:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{}Sniff.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.10,0:19:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{香取さんの言うとおりよ。}It's like Katori-san says.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.24,0:19:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{あなたたちはバレーを辞めちゃいけないわ。}You can't quit volleyball.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.23,0:19:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{XXバレーを愛してるのが本当なら…}Since your love for volleyball is true…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.64,0:19:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{なぜあたしたちはいがみ合ってるの？}…why do we even fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.66,0:19:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{なぜ手を合おってしないのよ。}Why aren't we united?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.10,0:19:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{小沢さん。それから、工藤さん、香取さん。}Ozawa-san. Kudou-san, Katori-san…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.12,0:19:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{お願いします。}Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.60,0:19:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしたちと一緒にチームを組んで…}Please make a team with us…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.97,0:19:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{あの親友のために。}…for the sake of that friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.71,0:20:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{鮎原さん。}Ayuhara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.25,0:20:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.92,0:20:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{それ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.57,0:20:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{あらちょっと。もう一つ。}Whoa. One more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.85,0:20:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{おい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.49,0:20:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.60,0:20:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{ほら頑張って！}Keep at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.85,0:20:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.68,0:20:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.58,0:20:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{それ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.82,0:20:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{可笑しいな。}Strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.21,0:20:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{親分、どうしたんだろ。}I wonder what chief's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.87,0:20:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{よし、XXXにしましょう。}All right, let's take a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.03,0:20:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{鮎原さんね、四天王を連れってくるつもりなのよ。}Ayuhara-san intends to get the Big Four back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.74,0:20:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{あそうか。}Ah, is that so.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.56,0:20:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{なるほど。}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.70,0:20:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{でもさ、今さらあんな連中にペコペコすることないじゃん？}Shouldn't they come to us bowing their heads by now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.64,0:20:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{XXX人たちでもないし、ね。}It won't be this simple. They have their pride, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.45,0:20:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{遅くに成りました。}Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.83,0:20:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{ーあら。\Nーまあ！。}- Hey.\N- Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.49,0:20:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{わあ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.70,0:20:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{参った。}Here she goes again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.33,0:20:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{何が言いたいんだろう。}You've got something to say, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.49,0:20:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{で？}Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.69,0:20:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{もともと、あたしたちが考えすぎたんです。}From the start we were thinking too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.78,0:21:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{ここに来たら、どうせXXXされるんだからって。}When we came here, we thought we'd be marginalized.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.71,0:21:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{それなら、先に主導権に握ってやろうって…}To avoid it, we decided to seize the initiative first.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.26,0:21:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{そう思ったです。}That's what we were thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.04,0:21:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{つまり、あたしたちようかほんの少し神経質だったのね。}In other words, you were a little nervous just like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.13,0:21:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{すみません。}We apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.23,0:21:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{失礼なこと言っちゃって…}We've been rude to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.71,0:21:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{へへへへ。}Hehehe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.68,0:21:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{何。分かれば良いんだよ。}Don't sweat it. We're over that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.39,0:21:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{スポーツマン、どうした。XXX行こう。}What's with you, sportsgirl. March with pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.61,0:21:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{ーはい。\Nーはい。}- Yes sir.\N- Yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.87,0:21:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{では、泉はどうした？}What about Izumi though?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.64,0:21:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{ーは…\Nーあの、それは…}- Ah, she…\N- Well that's…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.20,0:21:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{今日は学校の休んだらしいんだ。}Looks like she's absent from school today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.33,0:21:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしたちも気にしているんですけど。}We're worried about her as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.70,0:21:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{泉さんはこの二三日要すは可笑しかったから…}She's been acting strange since a few days ago…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.50,0:21:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{要すが？}Strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.83,0:21:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{そう言えば、何か隠したりみたいだったわ。}Now that you mention it, it feels like she was hiding something.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.06,0:21:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{だって、あなたたちは大の仲良しなんでしょう。}You're great friends. It must be for a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.84,0:21:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{それはさ…意外と秘密主義なのよう、彼女。}She's surprisingly secretive though.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.27,0:21:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{んん…}Hmm…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.99,0:21:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{無理ないわよ。泉さんの母さんて継母だから。}I can't blame her. Izumi-san's mom is actually her stepmother after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.74,0:21:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{継母…}A stepmother…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.00,0:21:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{後で行きます。きっと泉さんも分かってくれるわよね。}We'll tell her later. I'm sure she'll understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.76,0:21:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{うまく行くかな？彼女(XXX・無意義何と怖さら)ね。}I wonder if it goes well… she can be scary at times.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.59,0:21:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{んん。}Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.24,0:22:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{泉くんはいないと、四天王の意味はなくなるな。}Without Izumi-san, the name of Big Four loses its sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.18,0:22:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{その通りだわ。}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.51,0:22:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{先生。泉さんの家にあたしは行ってみます。}Professor. I'll go check on her and visit her home.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.09,0:22:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{ね、先生。}All right, professor?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.14,0:22:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{んん。}Hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.87,0:22:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{あら、じゃ、あたしたちも一緒に行きましょうか。}Ah. Let us go too then.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.77,0:22:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{あなたたちは練習、練習。}You should focus on practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.83,0:22:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたし一人で大丈夫よ。}I'll be fine by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.06,0:22:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{よし。じゃ、鮎原に行ってもらおう。}Very well. Let's leave it to Ayuhara.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.77,0:22:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}Yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.89,0:22:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{《泉》}《Izumi family》
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.75,0:22:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{大したお屋敷ね。}What a mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.51,0:22:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{ごめんください。}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.12,0:22:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{ごめんください。}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.43,0:22:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{お留守かしら？}I wonder if they're out.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.61,0:22:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{どなた？}Who might you be?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.20,0:22:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ、あの…泉ゆりさんいらっしゃいます？}Ah… I beg your pardon, is Izumi Yuri-san home?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.83,0:22:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ、ゆりのお友達？}Ah, you're Yuri's friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.17,0:22:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。鮎原こずえです。}Yes ma'am. My name's Ayuhara Kozue.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.18,0:22:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ、そうですか。どうぞ。}Ah, nice to meet you. Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.71,0:22:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{ゆりもう直ぐXXX。どうぞ。}Yuri will be home soon. Make yourself comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.66,0:22:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{すみません。}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.01,0:22:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{でも…}However…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.17,0:22:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{え？}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.98,0:22:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{あなた、バレー部の方じゃありませんわね？}You're not a member of the volleyball club, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.71,0:23:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{当たりました。そのバレー部なんです。}Spot on. I am its member.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.06,0:23:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{ごめんなさい。}I am very sorry…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.48,0:23:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{バレー部の方にはいただけないんです。}…but I'm afraid I can't let you meet with Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.10,0:23:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{え？}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.48,0:23:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{わざわざで来ましたも悪いんですけど、このまま帰っていただきません？}I'm sorry for troubling you with this request only now, but could you please go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.94,0:23:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ、なぜですか？あたし薮から棒にそんなこと言われても、あたし帰るわけにはいきません。}Ah… why's that? I came here out of the blue but I'd rather not go home until I meet with Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.16,0:23:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{なぜですか。}Why…?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.40,0:23:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{黙って帰って。}Shut up and go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.60,0:23:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ、泉さん。}Ah, Izumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.95,0:23:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{ゆり…}Yuri…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.11,0:23:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{帰ってよ。}Go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.54,0:23:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{ここはあんたのXXX所じゃないわ。}You're not welcome here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.22,0:23:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{早く。}Hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.29,0:23:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{帰ってたら。}Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.08,0:23:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{なぜ…}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.45,0:23:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{一体なぜなの？}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.49,0:23:54.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{こずえは一人泉の家を訪ねたが…}Kozue went alone to Izumi's home, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.24,0:23:58.67,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{バレー部の人間と分かったXX、泉の母の態度はXXXした。}…when it became evident she's with the volleyball club, Izumi's stepmother coldens.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.67,0:24:03.22,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{そこへ帰り合わせた泉ゆりはこずえの腕を掴んで、外へ追い立て。}After Izumi Yuri gets home, she grabs Kozue's arm and drags her out…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.22,0:24:06.58,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{母に大しても激しい言葉をXXX。}…shouting bitter words to her stepmother.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.58,0:24:11.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{こずえは泉親と何か深いわけがあるに違いないと思ったのだが…}Kozue can't shake off the feeling that there's something deeper going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.30,0:24:15.49,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{こんな態度に、こずえは思わずゆりの方に手は飛んだ。}But seeing Yuri's attitude, her hand reacts instinctively.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.49,0:24:19.06,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{さ、来週のアタックナンバーワンをお楽しみに。}Please look forward to the next episode.
